It is suggested that you download binary packages for your distros.

####
Installation from source:
####
tar -xjvf ho22bus-*.tar.bz2
cd ho22bus-*
./configure --prefix=/usr
make
sudo make install

####
Run the program:
####
ho22bus &
ho22bus -d &   // only run dict.


####
To install books and TTS sound files
####

Copy these files to ~/.ho22bus/books and ~/.ho22bus/TTS
       or prefix/share/ho22bus/books and prefix/share/ho22bus/TTS
See also ho22bus(1) .
